Show and pull available fields of a GitHub response.

Source: R/ghr_fields.R
ghr_fields.Rd

Show and pull available fields of a GitHub response.

ghr_fields(gh_response)

ghr_pull(gh_response, field)

ghr_path(gh_response)

ghr_html_url(gh_response)

ghr_download_url(gh_response)

Arguments

gh_response

A list object of class "gh_response".
field

Character string giving the name of the the element to extract from the github-response list.

Value

A character string.

See also

ghr_get gh_branches

Examples

gh_response <- ghr_get("hadley/babynames/data-raw")
ghr_fields(gh_response)
#>  [1] "name"         "path"         "sha"          "size"         "url"         
#>  [6] "html_url"     "git_url"      "download_url" "type"         "_links"      

ghr_pull(gh_response, "name")
#> [1] ".gitignore"            "applicants.R"          "applicants.csv"       
#> [4] "babynames_sample.csv"  "births.R"              "births.csv"           
#> [7] "lifetables.R"          "lifetables_sample.csv" "names.R"              
# Shortcuts
ghr_path(gh_response)
#> [1] "data-raw/.gitignore"            "data-raw/applicants.R"         
#> [3] "data-raw/applicants.csv"        "data-raw/babynames_sample.csv" 
#> [5] "data-raw/births.R"              "data-raw/births.csv"           
#> [7] "data-raw/lifetables.R"          "data-raw/lifetables_sample.csv"
#> [9] "data-raw/names.R"              
ghr_html_url(gh_response)
#> [1] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/.gitignore"           
#> [2] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/applicants.R"         
#> [3] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/applicants.csv"       
#> [4] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/babynames_sample.csv" 
#> [5] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/births.R"             
#> [6] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/births.csv"           
#> [7] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/lifetables.R"         
#> [8] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/lifetables_sample.csv"
#> [9] "https://github.com/hadley/babynames/blob/master/data-raw/names.R"              
ghr_download_url(gh_response)
#> [1] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/.gitignore"           
#> [2] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/applicants.R"         
#> [3] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/applicants.csv"       
#> [4] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/babynames_sample.csv" 
#> [5] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/births.R"             
#> [6] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/births.csv"           
#> [7] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/lifetables.R"         
#> [8] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/lifetables_sample.csv"
#> [9] "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hadley/babynames/master/data-raw/names.R"              

# Working with non-default branches
ghr_path(ghr_get("r-lib/usethis", ref = "gh-pages"))
#>  [1] "CNAME"                "CODE_OF_CONDUCT.html" "CONTRIBUTING.html"   
#>  [4] "ISSUE_TEMPLATE.html"  "LICENSE.html"         "SUPPORT.html"        
#>  [7] "articles"             "authors.html"         "dev"                 
#> [10] "docsearch.css"        "docsearch.js"         "index.html"          
#> [13] "link.svg"             "news"                 "pkgdown.css"         
#> [16] "pkgdown.js"           "pkgdown.yml"          "principles.html"     
#> [19] "reference"            "sitemap.xml"         
# Same
ghr_path(ghr_get("r-lib/usethis@gh-pages"))
#>  [1] "CNAME"                "CODE_OF_CONDUCT.html" "CONTRIBUTING.html"   
#>  [4] "ISSUE_TEMPLATE.html"  "LICENSE.html"         "SUPPORT.html"        
#>  [7] "articles"             "authors.html"         "dev"                 
#> [10] "docsearch.css"        "docsearch.js"         "index.html"          
#> [13] "link.svg"             "news"                 "pkgdown.css"         
#> [16] "pkgdown.js"           "pkgdown.yml"          "principles.html"     
#> [19] "reference"            "sitemap.xml"         
ghr_path(ghr_get("r-lib/usethis/news@gh-pages"))
#> [1] "news/index.html"
